These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, salsa
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of r&b is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | jazz     | r&b    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
