2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person eating peach is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Hobby   | camping     | skydiving | card-games |

