.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, german
1. the fan of trance is the canadian##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the german is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Nationality   | german    | canadian | dutch |

