The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, social-worker
1. the journalist is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating zucchini is in the middle##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
