3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| Pet   | hedgehog | chinchilla     | fish        |

