The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, pop
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of pop##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | camping | singing | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | country | pop     | house  |

